{"word":"H5525 - סֻכִּי - Çukkîy - sook-kee' - Sukkiims","slug":"H5525","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">סֻכִּי</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>Çukkîy"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>sook-kee'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Sukkiims"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E1;&#x05DB;&#x05BC;&#x05D9; - su&#x0302;kk&#x0131;&#x0302;y</b> - <i>sook-kee'</i><p/>Patrial from an unknown name (perhaps <a href=\"#/H5520\">H5520</a>); a <i>Sukkite</i>, or inhabitant of some place near Egypt (that is, <i>hut dwellers</i>): - Sukkiims."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4536\">H4536</a>, <a href=\"#/H5503\">H5503</a>, <a href=\"#/H5504\">H5504</a>, <a href=\"#/H5505\">H5505</a>, <a href=\"#/H5506\">H5506</a>, <a href=\"#/H5507\">H5507</a>, <a href=\"#/H5508\">H5508</a>, <a href=\"#/H5510\">H5510</a>, <a href=\"#/H5511\">H5511</a>, <a href=\"#/H5512\">H5512</a>, <a href=\"#/H5513\">H5513</a>, <a href=\"#/H5514\">H5514</a>, <a href=\"#/H5515\">H5515</a>, <a href=\"#/H5516\">H5516</a>, <a href=\"#/H5517\">H5517</a>, <a href=\"#/H5518\">H5518</a>, <a href=\"#/H5522\">H5522</a>, <a href=\"#/H5524\">H5524</a>"}]}